analysis_summary: Baseline semantic similarity established for initial TAS embeddings.

observations.details: Distinct clusters observed for 'Definition/Extraction', 'Embedding/Analysis', and 'Coordination/Reporting' TAS.
TAS within 'Definition/Extraction' (TAS1, TAS2, TAS3, TAS9, TAS10), 'Embedding/Analysis' (TAS4, TAS5, TAS7), and 'Coordination/Reporting' (TAS6, TAS8, TAS11) show strong internal semantic coherence.
